transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello. Hello. Yeah. Hanji. Hello, I'm audible, sir? Yes, sir, aapse baat hui thi na? To maine just mere manager ke cabin mein baat kara di. Thank you. Ji, ji, ji.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello, hanji. Hello.
Executive: Sir, actually main wohi puchti thi. Yeh jo dusra registration aap karne wale hain. Hum kuch form mein, original ke form mein kuch bhi matlab common hai, common owner or anything?
Customer: Nahi, nahi, kuch bhi common nahi hai usme.
Executive: Common owner nahi hai? Common hai ki main dono, main dono companies ke liye kaam karta hu, wohi common hai.
Executive: Matlab legal papers to kuch bhi common nahi hai, aap aisa keh rahe hain, jaise GST pe ya kuch bhi aisa.
Customer: Kuch bhi common nahi hai. Kuch bhi, kuch bhi common nahi hai dono companies mein.
Executive: Achha, theek hai. Sir, isme matlab documents vagarah GST mein like papers vagarah provide kar sakte hain?
Customer: Haan, haan, woh to maine sab usme dala bhi hua hai, GST vagarah sab provide hoga usme. Nahi, GST number dala hua hai, GST ke jo three page document hote hain na, woh aap share kar dijiye. Dusra main yeh jaanna chah rahi hu ki isme aap kaun sa package lena chah rahe hain?
